INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_0_IntroExotic: We're back. Because the Sour Bots locked up our friends. And, ok maybe we wanna get eaten again.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_0_IntroGummiL: Being eaten is the only way we can escape this dark place. But Sour Bots are trying to stop us from our dream of being chewed to a pulp.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_0_IntroSugarR: The Glitch moves fast. Help us escape by jump, jump, jumping to big Byte Mouth up top!
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_10_IntroDataM: We're not messing around this time. Fire away to take down the barriers and squash Sour Bots.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_11_IntroDataM: Those Sour Bots set up a firewall. Help us CRACK the firewalls like they're a tasty Crunchy Crawler.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_13_IntroGummi: Help us gather up five data chips. Shoot or jump on the Sour Bots to squash them. Like bugs.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_14_IntroGummi: Collect the data chips to bypass Pixel. Then help us die a glorious death from a giant Byte Mouth. Ahhh. Heaven.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_16_IntroCitri: We have to wiggle down deep to get eaten and escape. Guide us down to our delicious deaths!
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_17_IntroSugar: Jump, jump jump us up towards the beautiful Byte Mouth at the top of the level. Eat our Llama friend for unlimited jumps.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_18_IntroSugar: Uhhh. We are in trouble. The Sour Bots created a big scary glitch. If we get hit by the glitch, we'll regenerate as a new worm.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_19_IntroCitri: Stay away from those scary Sour Bots. Eat our Crunchy Crawler friends they disarm enemies.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_1_IntroExotic: Help us unlock our worm friends Crunchy Crawler, Octopus, Llama, Shark and Squiggle. They need to be eaten too.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_22_IntroCitri: The only way out of this deep dark tunnel is to guide us to the giant Byte Mouth at the bottom. Help us wiggle to our destiny. Please.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_2_IntroExotic: Find the keys, unlock our friends and bring them with us on our way to final Byte Mouth.
INPUT_IntroTextBox_Element_9_IntroDataMi: Crack the firewall, help us escape and guide us to our destiny to be eaten by a Byte Mouth!
